sentences: Ann-Sophie Dürmeyer (born 1 September 1990), better known as simply Ann Sophie, is a German singer and songwriter.
She represented Germany in the Eurovision Song Contest 2015 with the song "Black Smoke".
Her latest single "Phantom Pain" was released in November 2020.
